    "body": "Problem: Cmdline completion only shows match names, no description for\r\nthe highlighted command.\r\n\r\nSolution: Add a desc field to ex commands in ex_cmds.lua and nvim_get_commands\r\nshow selected commands desc when completeopt include \"popup\".\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\nVIMRUNTIME=~/workspace/neovim/runtime ~/workspace/neovim/build/bin/nvim --clean -u NONE \\\r\n-c 'set wildmode=noinsert:full' \\\r\n-c \"autocmd CmdlineChanged [:\\?] call wildtrigger()\" \\\r\n-c \"call nvim_create_user_command('SayHello', 'echo 222', {'desc': 'Say Hello'})\"\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"947\" height=\"496\" alt=\"test4\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9781f169-75a1-4ce4-b486-3f6a39cdb61e\" />\r\n",
    "closed_at": null,
